In addition, defense counsel shall inform the Court's Chambers by email by April 21, 2021, whether any of the Defendant's family members wish to attend the proceeding and whether they will attend in person or by phone. The Court will ensure access.

SO ORDERED.

Dated: April 19, 2021
New York, New York

ALISON J. NATHAN
United States District Judge
